com.vmware.esx.settings.depots

Interface OnlineTypes

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    Online
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    OnlineStub

    public interface OnlineTypes
    The Online interface provides methods to manage online software depots used during ESX lifecycle management.

    • Nested Class Summary

      Nested Classes

      static class  OnlineTypes._VAPI_OPERATIONS
      Identifiers of the task operations
      static class  OnlineTypes.CreateSpec
      The CreateSpec class defines the information used to create a depot.
      static class  OnlineTypes.DeleteResult
      The DeleteResult class contains a field that lists all the errors encountered after starting the task of Online.delete(java.lang.String) method.
      static class  OnlineTypes.FlushResult
      The FlushResult class contains a field that lists all the errors encountered after starting the task of com.vmware.esx.settings.depots.Online#flush method.
      static class  OnlineTypes.Info
      The Info class defines the information regarding a depot.
      static class  OnlineTypes.PrecheckResult
      The PrecheckResult class contains the fields that show the details of affected baselines and desired states found in Online.delete(java.lang.String) or com.vmware.esx.settings.depots.Online#flush operation.
      static class  OnlineTypes.Summary
      The Summary class defines the summary information regarding a depot.
      static class  OnlineTypes.UpdateSpec
      The UpdateSpec class defines the information used to update the depot.
